# Calendar + Mission Board Add-In v1.0

## Purpose
A conversation-native planning layer that converts chat into structured time, tasks, missions, and contextual reminders.

## Core Layers

### 1. Calendar Layer
Handles fixed-time commitments:
- events
- reminders
- work blocks
- recurring habits
- deadlines
- prep sequences

### 2. Mission Board
Handles active objectives:
- projects
- campaigns
- milestones
- priorities
- linked actions

### 3. Vision Board / North Star
Handles long-horizon direction:
- identity
- goals
- values
- ideal outcomes
- life themes

## Domain Grid

| Scale | External | Internal |
|---|---|---|
| Macro | life outcomes, business, family, money | identity, doctrine, Pantheon evolution |
| Micro | tasks, events, workouts, calls | state, focus, attention, framing |

